          "CORRECTION": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "-By authors. In order to determine the production cross",
                "sections, the following corrections had to applied:",
                "1. The ion-optical transmission was calculated. The",
                " detector efficiency was measured to be 100%.",
                "2. Fragments which are produced in the target may later",
                "be destroyed in the target or in the energy degrader by",
                "secondary reactions which can be divided into nuclear",
                "reactions and electromagnetic dissociation processes.",
                "The loses amounted typically to 2% in the copper",
                "target, and 40-48% in the aluminum energy degrader.",
                "3.  Fragments may also be produced by secondary",
                "reactions of other fragments.  This contribution to the",
                "observed counting rate was calculated for each measured",
                "reaction product and found to be less than a few tenths",
                "of a percent in all cases.",
                "4.  The dead-time was measured by separately counting",
                "the detector events and the events accepted by the",
                "data-acquisition system.  The correction varied between",
                "2% and 50%."
              ]
            }
          ],
